parameters:
Kru: "No way, what's up with this forest... It's so vast and the climb is
killing me..."

Kru: "Phew... But did all those who didn't return die in this forest? There
aren't any monsters strong enough to kill someone though..."

Kru: "Well, it's about obtaining immortality. I guess it wouldn't be worth
it without a trial of this level..."
Kru: "But immortality, huh... Do I really want to live that long...?"
Kru: "A girl's voice No way In the depths of the forest like this"
Kru: "Anyway, I've got to go help"
Umi: "Don't... suddenly get up like that!"
When I looked up, there was a girl...

Red hair, red eyes, and a frown on her forehead... her emotions were also
red...

The vividness of that color erased the background from my consciousness,
erased my thoughts, and as if left behind by time, my existence came to a
halt...

Umi: "It's not 'what'! I was worried because you were collapsed here, so I
called out to you..."
Umi: "Hmph! By the way, have you seen a cat around here?"
Kru: "A cat? No, I haven't seen one..."
Kru: "She's gone... What was that all about...?"
What in the world... was that...?
Kru: "A girl's voice! Was it that girl from before"
